# Website Reverse-Engineer Template

## What This Is
A reusable template for reverse-engineering any website and rebuilding it as a faithful clone using Cursor Agent. The Next.js + shadcn/ui + Tailwind v4 base is pre-scaffolded — fill in `TARGET.md` and run `/clone-website`.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router, React 19, TypeScript strict)
- **UI:** shadcn/ui (Radix primitives, Tailwind CSS v4, `cn()` utility)
- **Icons:** Lucide React (default — replaced/supplemented by extracted SVGs)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 with oklch design tokens
- **Deployment:** Vercel

## Commands
- `npm run dev` — Start dev server
- `npm run build` — Production build
- `npm run lint` — ESLint check
